                  faq_ans:
                    "It takes time to see results for hair loss. At Traya, we treat your concerns inside out. Generally, individuals in the initial stages of hair loss may begin to see volume gain and hair regrowth in around 5-6 months. However, the treatment duration is influenced by factors such as your specific hair loss stage, age, root causes, underlying health conditions and more.\n\nTraya's treatment typically progresses through three phases:\nPhase 1: Early signs of improvement in root causes, such as digestion, sleep quality, gut health, and energy levels\nPhase 2: Improvement in scalp and follicle health, leading to reduced hair fall\nPhase 3: Emergence of new baby hair growth\n\nConsistency in treatment is key to see positive results. If you have still not seen results within the prescribed time period even after being completely regular with the treatment, you can talk to a Hair Coach and they shall help you with the best course of action.",
